<paragraph blockId="11.[151,1437,1305,1692]" pageId="11" pageNumber="354">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[199,449,1341,1368]" pageId="11" pageNumber="354">Original description:</emphasis>
“statura più piccola della precedente” [shell shorter than the previous one— 
<taxonomicName authority="(Philippi, 1844)" authorityName="Philippi" authorityYear="1844" baseAuthorityName="Philippi" baseAuthorityYear="1844" class="Gastropoda" family="Clathurellidae" genus="Clathromangelia" kingdom="Animalia" order="Neogastropoda" pageId="11" pageNumber="354" phylum="Mollusca" rank="species" species="granum">
<emphasis italics="true" pageId="11" pageNumber="354">Clathromangelia granum</emphasis>
(
<bibRefCitation author="Philippi, R. A." box="[316,480,1377,1403]" pageId="11" pageNumber="354" refId="ref18455" refString="Philippi, R. A. (1844) Fauna Molluscorum viventium et in tellure tertiaria fossilium regni utriusque Siciliae. Enumeratio Molluscorum Siciliae cum viventium tum in tellure tertiaria fossilium, quae in itinere suo observavit - Volumen secundum. Sumptibus Eduardi Anton, Halis Saxorum, 303 pp." type="book" year="1844">Philippi, 1844</bibRefCitation>
)
</taxonomicName>
, reported as 
<taxonomicName authority=", Phil." authorityName="Phil." box="[630,982,1377,1404]" class="Gastropoda" family="Clathurellidae" genus="Clathromangilia" kingdom="Animalia" order="Neogastropoda" pageId="11" pageNumber="354" phylum="Mollusca" rank="species" species="granum">
<emphasis box="[630,910,1377,1403]" italics="true" pageId="11" pageNumber="354">Clathromangilia granum</emphasis>
, Phil.
</taxonomicName>
].
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
<subSubSection pageId="11" pageNumber="354" type="discussion">
<paragraph blockId="11.[151,1437,1305,1692]" pageId="11" pageNumber="354">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[199,317,1414,1440]" pageId="11" pageNumber="354">Remarks:</emphasis>
having been instituted as named after Carlo Praus Franceschini, we rank it subspecific, and thus available (
<bibRefCitation author="ICZN &amp; International Commission on Zoological Nomenclature" box="[268,404,1449,1475]" pageId="11" pageNumber="354" refId="ref17437" refString="ICZN [International Commission on Zoological Nomenclature] (2012) International code of zoological nomenclature. 4 th Edition. International Trust for Zoological Nomenclature, London. Available from: http: // www. iczn. org / (accessed 15 Feburary 2019)" type="url" year="2012">ICZN 2012</bibRefCitation>
: Art. 10, glossary). 
<bibRefCitation author="Praus Franceschini, C." box="[628,925,1449,1476]" pageId="11" pageNumber="354" pagination="1 - 68" refId="ref18743" refString="Praus Franceschini, C. (1906) Elenco delle conchiglie del Golfo di Napoli e del Mediterraneo esistenti nel Museo Zoologico di Napoli. Annuario del Museo Zoologico della R. Universita di Napoli, 2 (5), 1 - 68." type="journal article" year="1906">Praus Franceschini (1906)</bibRefCitation>
listed this taxon as a variety of 
<taxonomicName authority="(Philippi, 1844)" authorityName="Philippi" authorityYear="1844" baseAuthorityName="Philippi" baseAuthorityYear="1844" class="Gastropoda" family="Clathurellidae" genus="Clathromangelia" kingdom="Animalia" order="Neogastropoda" pageId="11" pageNumber="354" phylum="Mollusca" rank="species" species="granum">
<emphasis italics="true" pageId="11" pageNumber="354">Clathromangelia granum</emphasis>
(
<bibRefCitation author="Philippi, R. A." box="[317,481,1485,1511]" pageId="11" pageNumber="354" refId="ref18455" refString="Philippi, R. A. (1844) Fauna Molluscorum viventium et in tellure tertiaria fossilium regni utriusque Siciliae. Enumeratio Molluscorum Siciliae cum viventium tum in tellure tertiaria fossilium, quae in itinere suo observavit - Volumen secundum. Sumptibus Eduardi Anton, Halis Saxorum, 303 pp." type="book" year="1844">Philippi, 1844</bibRefCitation>
)
</taxonomicName>
. However, material belonging to this taxon was deposited in MZF2 by himself, thus not constituting the original 
<typeStatus box="[477,539,1522,1548]" pageId="11" pageNumber="354">types</typeStatus>
, and was also not found during current research. 
<bibRefCitation author="Bellini, R." box="[1108,1281,1521,1547]" pageId="11" pageNumber="354" pagination="1 - 87" refId="ref15827" refString="Bellini, R. (1929 a) I molluschi del Golfo di Napoli (studi precedenti, l'ambiente, enumerazione e sinonimia). Annuario del Museo Zoologico della R. Universita di Napoli, 6 (2), 1 - 87." type="journal article" year="1929">Bellini (1929a)</bibRefCitation>
subsequently reported it as 
<taxonomicName authority="Monteros." authorityName="Monteros." box="[303,840,1557,1584]" class="Gastropoda" family="Clathurellidae" genus="Clathromangilia" kingdom="Animalia" order="Neogastropoda" pageId="11" pageNumber="354" phylum="Mollusca" rank="variety" species="granum" variety="prausis">
<emphasis box="[303,582,1557,1583]" italics="true" pageId="11" pageNumber="354">Clathromangilia granum</emphasis>
var. 
<emphasis box="[636,718,1558,1583]" italics="true" pageId="11" pageNumber="354">prausis</emphasis>
Monteros.
</taxonomicName>
in his general overview of the marine molluscan species living in the Gulf of Naples. Taking into account its telegraphic description, as well as the figure attached to it, 
<taxonomicName authority="Bellini, 1902" authorityName="Bellini" authorityYear="1902" box="[151,715,1629,1656]" class="Gastropoda" family="Clathurellidae" genus="Clathromangilia" kingdom="Animalia" order="Neogastropoda" pageId="11" pageNumber="354" phylum="Mollusca" rank="variety" species="granum" variety="prausi">
<emphasis box="[151,432,1629,1655]" italics="true" pageId="11" pageNumber="354">Clathromangilia granum</emphasis>
var. 
<emphasis box="[489,561,1630,1655]" italics="true" pageId="11" pageNumber="354">prausi</emphasis>
<bibRefCitation author="Bellini, R." box="[568,715,1629,1655]" pageId="11" pageNumber="354" pagination="85 - 121" refId="ref15636" refString="Bellini, R. (1902 a) Contribuzione alla conoscenza della fauna dei molluschi marini dell'isola di Capri. Bollettino della Societa dei Naturalisti in Napoli, Series 1, 15, 85 - 121." type="journal article" year="1902">Bellini, 1902</bibRefCitation>
</taxonomicName>
may easily fit several Mediterranean raphitomid taxa, often not even congeneric, and thus it is considered a 
<emphasis box="[645,811,1665,1691]" italics="true" pageId="11" pageNumber="354">nomen dubium</emphasis>
(
<bibRefCitation author="ICZN &amp; International Commission on Zoological Nomenclature" box="[825,959,1665,1691]" pageId="11" pageNumber="354" refId="ref17437" refString="ICZN [International Commission on Zoological Nomenclature] (2012) International code of zoological nomenclature. 4 th Edition. International Trust for Zoological Nomenclature, London. Available from: http: // www. iczn. org / (accessed 15 Feburary 2019)" type="url" year="2012">ICZN 2012</bibRefCitation>
: glossary).
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
